These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, pakistani, egyptian
1. the pakistani is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking juice is the egyptian##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee | juice   |
| Nationality      | malaysian    | pakistani  | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, tea
House: ranch-style, craftsman, futuristic
1. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
3. the craftsman house is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta     | tea      |
| House   | craftsman | ranch-style | futuristic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, mechanic, manager
There 3 different types of food: plum, radish, raspberry
1. the mechanic is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the manager is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the paramedic is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Job   | paramedic | manager  | mechanic       |
| Food       | plum     | radish | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, boat, jet-ski
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, woodworking
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Transport    | jet-ski    | boat     | bike |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | puzzles     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, purple, light-blue
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person who likes ebony is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Color         | purple | ebony     | light-blue |
| Transport   | van        | airplane | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, police-officer, architect
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train
1. the videographer is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the police-officer is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the architect is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Job        | architect | videographer      | police-officer  |
| Transport   | boat       | motorbike | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, salsa
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, vegafina, old-henry
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of r&b is the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the havana-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | jazz     | r&b    |
| Cigar           | havana | old-henry | vegafina |

 #################################

 
