.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, puzzles
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, cola
1. the person drinking sprite is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | filmmaking | chess  |
| Beverage     | cola     | sprite      | juice |

