1. the person who likes azure is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the security-guard is on the left of the electrician##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | coach    | security-guard | electrician |
| Color   | azure | orange     | pink        |

