.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, nectarine, papaya
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, grey, blood-red
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
2. the person eating garlic is the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | nectarine | papaya   | garlic        |
| Color   | grey    | blue | blood-red |

