.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, fanta
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, house, pop
1. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of pop##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of pop##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | lemonade | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | country | pop     | house  |

